node.text:
Wow a year went by like a flash...
I am so lucky to have an incredibly supportive amazing wife by my side that helps me every step of the way in my career!
I love you @amberrosebarcia happy 1st wedding anniversary!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by JUSTIN BARCIA on July 18, 2021. May be an image of 4 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text:
What a weekend 😎
Words aren’t enough to express how grateful I am for the crew I have in my corner! 
Family, Team, Fans everyone thanks for always believing in me let’s go get some more wins ☝🏻❤️
